against the abuse of prisoners this year that situation continues when detainee huynh duc thanh_binh another patriotic student was beaten along with others xuan loc detention center dong nai _since the end of there were more people arrested for exercising their right to free expression _they are freelance journalist pham chi_dung youtuber nguyen van nghiem activist tran duc thach journalist pham van blogger nguyen tuong thuy according to unofficial report there are more than political prisoners have been unlawfully detained in vietnam since january and there are still plenty of cases of detainment without trial any vietnamese activists would endure and face the hardship of being harassed beaten imprisoned and brought to closed trial where family the public of the detainees are not allowed to attend think that my work as an activist even in exile is not yet done recounting all hardship and loss suffered by victims of the communism would require us to publish endless volumes of books myself lucky enough to have the support of the international community that able to share my own story with you _but other mothers such as ms _doan thi hong who took to the street to protest against the vietnam special economic zone lease project _she was forcefully separated from her year old daughter and imprisoned without trial until nowlife in prison is an countless chain of difficult days suffering from physical and mental abuse being separated from the outside world facing difficulties against every family visit _these are some of the predicament that political prisoners in seminars every year that we can continue to stand up for the victims in states of oppresion and those imprisoned by the communist regimes ladies and gentlemen know that there are many human rights violations happening around the world as every day goes by and vietnam is country in your focus would ask you to focus on your voice of concern that created platform to protect vietnamese detainees who are in need the most and would send strong message to the communist authorities that they must be cautious of your reports and demands in addition would like to emphasize that your efforts to fight for freedom for those who have been imprisoned also has positive effects on those who are active and not yet arrested _it has given them the necessary assurance that the world is always watching
